OL,3,CMotorbike rider dies after crash on
OL,4,CA72 in the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FA motorbike rider has died following a
OL,7,Fcrash in the Scottish Borders.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to A72
OL,10,Fnear Innerleithen at around 12.40pm on
OL,11,FSaturday, 11 April to a collision
OL,12,Fbelieved to involve a black Yamaha YBR
OL,13,F125 motorbike, a grey Citroen C4
OL,14,FPicasso and a yellow Citroen DS3.
OL,16,FThe Yamaha rider, a 53-year-old man,
OL,17,Fdied at the scene. No other injuries
OL,18,Fwere reported.
OL,20,FThe road was closed for most of the
OL,21,Fday and reopened at around 9pm.
