OL,3,CMotorbike rider dies after crash on
OL,4,CA72 in the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FPolice Scotland are investigating the
OL,7,Fincident and have appealed for
OL,8,Fwitnesses.
OL,10,FSergeant Dave Waddell said: "Our
OL,11,Fthoughts are with the family and
OL,12,Ffriends of the man who has died.
OL,14,F"Enquiries are ongoing and we are
OL,15,Fappealing to anyone who witnessed the
OL,16,Fcrash to contact us. We would like to
OL,17,Fthank the members of the public who
OL,18,Fassisted at the scene of the crash.
